data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 3-bedroom 2-bathroom home in Coon Rapids! This home comes equipped with an expansive fenced in backyard, large bonfire pit, and a spacious deck. Moving inside to the main level you will find the large living room, dining room, full bathroom, a spacious kitchen, and 3 bedrooms, one of which includes a walk-in closet. Moving down to the lower level you will find a ¾ bathroom, a large family room perfect for entertaining, and the spacious laundry/utility room. This home is located just minutes away from multiple parks, Green Haven Golf Course, and must try restaurants and shopping spots. Don't miss your chance to call this house your home!
